{"tid":1886870,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[Sir. This way]華為 控告美國政府阻商業活動 敗訴","createTime":"2020-02-19T07:52:29.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-19T08:42:03.000Z","uid":284699,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"d1d428fcd8e3440df13e2a0e618ea6196d429261","tid":1886870,"uid":284699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-19T07:52:29.000Z","msg":"【e-zone 專訊】美國聯邦法院就華為訟訴美國限制參與政府商業活動的提訟被判敗訴，華為對判決失望，並表示尋求其他法律行動。<br />\n<br />\n華為敗訴表示會考慮其他方法<br />\n美政府表示滿意<br />\n華為被美政府「禁足」參與任何聯邦政府相關商業活動，早前該公司入稟提告，法院美國時間本周二（2 月 18 日）下達 57 頁判詞，表示美國國會有權力就國防授權法去採取相關行動。相關行動，除了華為，被禁足的亦包括另一家電訊設備商中興通訊。<br />\n<br />\n華為發言人對判決失望，表示了解國家安全的重要性，但美國政府去年引用 NDAA 時，損害了華為的權利，是錯誤的保護主義想法，華為會繼續考慮其他的法律選項。至於美國政府則表示對判決滿意。<br />\n<br />\nSource：路透社"},{"pid":"c6c970181aa99a40feb3146b0025b4ab3848a8a9","tid":1886870,"uid":66202,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-19T07:56:07.000Z","msg":"God bless America<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"19776afbc74f663033d8c4782ee27df34232c9b7","tid":1886870,"uid":1251,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-19T08:00:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> USA"},{"pid":"ef00fbc58b77ac06643ec0564fc2d69ef5daa286","tid":1886870,"uid":104804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-19T08:02:23.000Z","msg":"GOOGLE FB幾時入到中國市場<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eca1ddba46f8364dd27bcbef7870468b76872750","tid":1886870,"uid":61974,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-19T08:04:58.000Z","msg":"咁都比你告得入，真係over全美國人dead body"},{"pid":"d48c76146e5f055ca57d315acd491bfae45fbf1b","tid":1886870,"uid":286792,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-19T08:17:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d7c176085ce3c54447cad9c2350ffdcfc35a1bf1","tid":1886870,"uid":249263,"like":0,"disli